&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;FM Central Administrator - Band 3 within FM Operational Services Central Administration Team.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;CANDIDATES WHO HAD PREVIOUSLY APPLIED AND BEEN UNSUCCESSFUL FOR THIS POSITION NEED NOT APPLY AGAIN.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The FM Operational Services Central Admin Team are seeking a flexible, enthusiatic and hardworking individual to work as a Helpdesk Administrator. Based in the new super hospital at Southmead you will be the first point of contact for all Trust staff to log requests for services from Estate Management, Porters, Domestics, Catering, Laundry and Waste Management.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We are looking for someone with an excellent telephone manner and good customer service/communication skills. The successful candidate will need to be able to work quickly and accurately under pressure and work as part of a team.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Full time role available, working Monday to Friday on a rotating pattern, 37.5 hrs per week. The shift pattern will be:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Mon-Fri&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;6am - 2pm (2 weeks)&lt;br /&gt;2pm - 10pm (2 weeks)&lt;br /&gt;10pm - 6am (1 week)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The rota will be subject to review and could change to better suit service delivery if required.&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;There may be an initial training period so flexibility to undertake training will be required. Training will be organised on job acceptance for the successful candidate.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Band 3 pay scale: £19,737 - £21,142 per annum pro rata for those meeting the full requirements of the post as detailed in the person specification excluding unsocial hours or overtime payments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameNuno CruzJob titleFM Central Admin Team LeaderEmail addressnuno.cruz@nbt.nhs.ukTelephone number01174141136Additional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Nuno Cruz&lt;/strong&gt; Nuno.Cruz@nbt.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
